{"tid":1616781,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［抵制 人一藍腦便殘］都市日報行政總裁， 搵樓王 admin 曹雪聰","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:10:49.000Z","uid":316236,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99b184ec5f667a78888c64230694a4182b25a7d1","tid":1616781,"uid":316236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"[已FC] 呢隻曹姓光頭佬深藍到發紫，做個腦殘時事評論員。平時見你條撚屌發表埋好多同業務無關的新聞評論博出位都算數，頂盡政見唔同。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來仆你個街條友係一啲良心都冇 冇道德 泯滅人性（睇佢同何妖影相就知唔係咩好人）。 係自己做嘅搵樓王fb page尻up就知佢藍到紫，講野淨係識煽動仇恨，鼓吹暴力。之前將&ldquo;願榮光歸香港&rdquo; 做&quot;願平安歸香港&quot; . <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係老細寫定點 但能夠容忍下屬的貼文 作為老細的曹雪聰一定有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為網站登記人(IP) 同聲稱係 搵樓王 顧問 唔好同我講你無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要同何妖有關係 種唔斷正 握曬手咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港有咁既傳媒人真係好不幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家上FB Page睇下: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FindHouse.HongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFindHouse.HongKong%2F&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=05c377a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FindHouse.HongKong/</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請即 Report 佢個網! 不繼click 佢既廣告立即關閉視窗!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1j45C2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1j45C2G.png&h=3256d05a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKyidA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKyidA2.png&h=ec595d87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q9Srnuo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq9Srnuo.png&h=4ed56ab2&s={SIZE}\" 